title: Poets Of The Fall - Theme Songs (Unreleased).rar
description:
Exclusively themes songs from the Finnish Rock band created for game soundtracks and series such Heroes, Alan Wake, Death Rally an many more.
I got all songs renamed from Wikipedia. So the songs are real but unreleased in a cd, so I made a cd with those theme songs. Very cool! Must have for the fans of Alan Wake and Poets of the Fall (Aka Old Gods of Asgard) Cover included.

Enjoy and keep seeding! ;)
